lead_paragraph: Erik Compton birdied three of five holes to take a share of the lead with Jason Day early in the third round of the rain-plagued Zurich Classic in Avondale, La.

headline.print_headline: Two Lead With 13 Under as Rain Gets in the Way
headline.main: Two Share Lead in Zurich Classic

snippet: Erik Compton birdied three of five holes to take a share of the lead with Jason Day early in the third round of the rain-plagued Zurich Classic in Avondale, La.
abstract: Erik Compton and Jason Day share third round lead at Zurich Classic golf tournament; other golf news noted.
